Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:08.11,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one by the name of \NCharlotte E Firobisher in the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.03,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:14.95,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:21.08,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness... Father did not recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.83,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn’t recognize Mother or me as his family?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.13,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.88,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:38.01,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\pos(630,523)}Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:38.01,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur4\pos(194,766)}Departure –Resolution–
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:43.56,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there nothing we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:51.03,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, as a city we can’t go against the order to deliver them to the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:56.61,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s horrible! The Empire said that they would be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:01:00.08,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly, the Empire is in the wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:04.66,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re intentionally trying to erase Charlotte’s existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:09.54,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re not foolish enough to believe \Nevery word coming from the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:13.34,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should firmly refuse delivering them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.76,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll protect Charlotte in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:19.64,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don’t ask for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.81,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empire is treating them as criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:30.73,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving them shelter wouldn’t come without endangering the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:36.07,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,B–But we’re the only ones who \Ncan save Charlotte and the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:41.45,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Cecily! This is a serious political issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.28,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.45,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want this city to wage war against the Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.04,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.93,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember, Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:03.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The words I said when I faced Jack Strader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:06.18,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.85,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,was that you would protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.81,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:20.36,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte, dear, it’s bad for your health if you don’t eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.03,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not hungry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:27.58,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Lady Charlotte. This meat is really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.12,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.54,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.84,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.85,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fine. This was clearly a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:50.89,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. The Empire would never abandon Lady Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:58.99,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect you. I’m sure everything \Nwill turn out all right so please, don’t cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:20.13,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a mess, Cecily. Drawing water is basic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can’t even pull that off, then your future is bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.14,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re one to say, with that much training...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:32.39,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, if you don’t get stronger, \Nyou can’t protect those important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.15,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I’ve got an egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.36,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll cheer up Lady Charlotte with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.70,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs are a good source of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.57,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I’m getting some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.07,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, they can’t lay that many eggs at—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.49,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll make them lay more eggs with my spirit! My spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.08,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:58.84,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,They will be punished under the Imperial Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.61,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seek refuge in a militaristic state?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.90,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems to be our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.49,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The country said they accept those conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.28,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.29,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.45,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t consent to becoming refugees!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.92,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll say it once more: There’s no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:43.22,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that way, all we’re doing is \Ncornering Charlotte and the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.09,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you think of something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.01,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:47.84,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.93,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empire already mobilized the army. We’re under serious pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:58.94,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus far he has yet to make a move, \Nbut we can’t tell when they’ll become hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:04.44,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand that we can not give them a pretext to assault this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:13.91,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will return the four captured magic swords \Nand report to the Empire that you have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.29,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you let us escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.13,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empire will blame us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:24.97,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it should be fine if I apologize \Nas the Captain of the Knight Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.76,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do that much for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:33.52,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the very best we can do as a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:39.19,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the militaristic state won’t accept us unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:46.95,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The conditions are that you offer the military all you know about the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.87,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,To betray the Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:55.54,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Betray our motherland?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:58.87,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,How will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.38,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t answer that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.59,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecily, do you also agree with us seeking refuge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.18,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:16.48,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn’t come here to flee to a martial dictatorship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.90,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can’t return to the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.52,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.99,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we shelter you, we’ll endanger this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:33.49,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to put the weight of your lives and this town on Cecily’s shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:40.25,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want you to die. I don’t want to let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.50,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We live, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:49.38,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that we should discard Mother’s wish and sell out the Empire just to live longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.97,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that I should choose that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.68,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.18,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.14,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We want Lady Charlotte to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.98,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t stand for refuge or anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.56,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Lady Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.15,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.62,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.12,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say they have nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.38,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that pain all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:28.59,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe anything is better than dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.97,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could make Charlotte and the others see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.26,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.39,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:40.23,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling them not to die without giving them a reason to live isn’t persuasive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.56,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,A reason to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:45.02,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to happen to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:48.53,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be satisfied with just ridding this town of a nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:53.45,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I just want Charlotte and the others to live happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:59.83,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,To eat with everyone and laugh... That’s all I really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:04.21,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,But they can’t live in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:09.59,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,They can’t return to the Empire either. And thinking they’d take refuge in the militaristic state is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:18.85,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it were me, as long as I could be with Luke and Cecily, I wouldn’t mind where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:24.23,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it in the Empire or in the militaristic state, as long as I can be like this with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.23,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.23,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that’s right! It’s exactly that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.82,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer was already in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.20,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you convey that properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.32,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can convey it, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.66,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You better hurry, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:44.50,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t tell what a cornered person will do once provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:54.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,If only there was a way to make the Empire recognize Lady Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.76,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.01,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve made our decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.52,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll just do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.48,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,For Lady Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:14.90,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.95,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecily hasn’t returned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.74,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doris and the girls, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.75,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Charlotte, my dear, \Ndo you know where everyone is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.37,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.84,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing in this rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.39,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Penelope!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.01,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone’s there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.89,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The guards were all supposed to be put asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.07,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecily?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.95,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:07.08,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t want to believe it and I wanted to be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.71,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still make it. Return to the mansion with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.71,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that won’t do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:18.93,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our only choice. Bringing the \Nmagic sword and the Blacksmith as gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.22,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re returning to the Empire with Lady Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:26.98,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down your heads! Did Charlotte wish for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:31.73,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but we don’t want to see \NLady Charlotte sad any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.19,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.53,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to hear that from you, \Nyou incompetent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.49,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.70,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m incompetent, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.79,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.50,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.59,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t leave no matter what, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then fetch your magic swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.18,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be unfair to be the \Nonly one with a magic sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.72,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.18,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn’t adhere to reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:12.35,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there’s a handicap? \NWe’ve beaten you to a pulp before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.73,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.48,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.48,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don’t get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.15,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will say it out loudly this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.11,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.58,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers, Cecily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:39.84,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, besides being stupid, I’m also stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.26,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhomphaia’s range is infinite. There’s no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.52,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no use in doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.06,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind, pierce through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:10.95,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,If a sword is used as a spear, it can pierce anything. \NYou taught me that technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.75,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Margot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.09,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to Margot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.94,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can beat me in close combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.27,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.94,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.78,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,What terrible rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:56.33,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked around, but couldn’t find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.21,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:03.84,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about strange, the storehouse was \Nwide open and a few weapons were missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.97,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,My, could it be a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.47,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.73,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doris! Margot! Penelope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:26.65,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:31.66,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic sword’s power won’t work on the Bollock Knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:38.00,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but casting wind from it’s \Nblade isn’t all there is to a magic sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.80,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.97,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.52,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t defeat you in close combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.98,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic wind won’t work either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:08.61,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will become the arrow that pierces you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.99,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the decision I made with Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.12,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.58,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Penelope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.71,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecily, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.21,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’re here. Let’s settle the score!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.92,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.09,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doris...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.64,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely take Aria, even if \NI have to change her personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:38.56,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You think the Empire will accept \NCharlotte if you bring the magic sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.19,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the best way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.48,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.36,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:49.74,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! We want Lady Charlotte to smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:55.45,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we can do! Please understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.79,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.54,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empire will kill Charlotte! They will never save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.71,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empire abandoned her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.92,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:08.59,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should also abandon the Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.97,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Discard the name of “E!”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.72,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,And think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:19.02,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of a way of making Charlotte happy! \NThe four of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.19,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.53,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make Lady Charlotte’s dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:35.33,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.60,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doris! Margot! Penelope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.48,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.65,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take refuge in the militaristic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.36,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then what of Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.49,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my only reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.53,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I live from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.45,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:24.42,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,These three were desperate for your sake. \NAnd you still can’t see anything besides your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.67,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Doris and the girls nothing more than servants to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:32.30,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Doris and the girls are my precious—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.43,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. Your family is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.60,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Start a new life, with the four of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:47.27,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I should betray the Empire, my Mother’s will, and live in shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.73,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong with living in shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:57.95,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how, just live, survive, and grasp your own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:02.04,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that’s the way to comply with every wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.54,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I should take refuge, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:10.42,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you decline, then take your blade and fight for your own future!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:26.73,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make Mother happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.98,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be connected with Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.32,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:02.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, Charlotte E Firobisher is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.85,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:35.09,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empire has taken the four magic swords and withdrawn. There’s nothing to worry about anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.55,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m thankful for the mayor’s arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:42.97,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I also apologize for the trouble I have brought upon you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.23,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to Luke as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:47.98,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:53.23,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte, dear, here’s some \Nfood to share with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.94,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my masterpiece. Savor it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.32,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.36,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.49,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.83,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, all right? And don’t be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.08,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.21,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we won’t have our big-breasted toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.34,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what you have to say in the very end?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.55,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will also grow fine breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.14,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.51,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Cecily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.68,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s meet somewhere again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.31,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.15,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cecily, I will tell you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:40.78,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a man who gave us the four magic swords and incited us to come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.86,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.32,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Siegfried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.83,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Siegfried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.62,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s rumored to train strange beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.62,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte, let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.42,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.00,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you for your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.63,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.42,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:03.38,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a fine family. There’s nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.68,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.27,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll discard the name of “E.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:20.48,BlasmiMD1,,0000,0000,0000,,I salute the mother who gave birth to you and the three who’ve raised you.
